# === Account: quasimorphic ===
IMAPAccount quasimorphic
Host witcher.mxrouting.net
Port 993
User alan@quasimorphic.com
PassCmd "rbw get 'Quasimorphic Email'"
TLSType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore quasimorphic-remote
Account quasimorphic

MaildirStore quasimorphic-local
SubFolders Verbatim
Path ~/.mail/quasimorphic/
Inbox ~/.mail/quasimorphic/Inbox

Channel quasimorphic
Far :quasimorphic-remote:
Near :quasimorphic-local:
Patterns *
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *

# === Account: broad ===
IMAPAccount broad
Host imap.gmail.com
Port 993
User amunozgo@broadinstitute.org
PassCmd "rbw get 'Broad Email App Password'"
TLSType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt
AuthMechs LOGIN

IMAPStore broad-remote
Account broad

MaildirStore broad-local
SubFolders Verbatim
Path ~/.mail/broad/
Inbox ~/.mail/broad/Inbox

Channel broad
Far :broad-remote:
Near :broad-local:
Patterns * !"[Gmail]/All Mail"
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *
